snippet.title: 2 OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
2 is a spiritual successor to a game i made five years ago
this is a game about exploring. it is available for windows, macintosh, and probably linux with some effort.

https://hubol.itch.io/2

i put two years of my life into this game. i have noticed myself grow and watched my friends grow as i designed this game. i hope that you like it. i am very proud of it
